%% AI Politician Accountability System
flowchart LR
  subgraph Collection[Data Collection]
    UL[User Location Module (Python)] --> ON[OpenNorth API Fetcher]
  end

  ON --> MQ[Message Queue / Task Queue]

  subgraph Manager[Deep Research Manager]
    MQ --> MGR[Manager / Orchestrator]
    MGR --> A1[Political Activities Agent]
    MGR --> A2[Personal Controversies Agent]
    MGR --> A3[Voting Record & Policy Agent]
  end

  A1 --> SUP[Supervisor Agent (aggregates HTML & meta)]
  A2 --> SUP
  A3 --> SUP

  SUP --> DB[Raw HTML Store (DB / Blob Storage)]
  SUP --> EMB[Embedding Service / Vector DB]
  SUP --> SUM[Summarizer LLM]

  SUM --> ADT[Adult Summary Service (semi-formal)]
  SUM --> KID[Kid Summary Service (slang, fine-tuned LLM)]

  ADT --> UIAdult[Adult UI (web/mobile)]
  KID --> UIKid[Kid UI (engaging, age-appropriate)]

  subgraph Ops[Infrastructure & Ops]
    SCHED[Scheduler / Cron] --> MGR
    MON[Monitoring & Audit Logs] --> DB
    CACHE[Embedding Cache] --> SUM
    FT[Fine-tune Pipeline] --> KID
    AUTH[Auth & Rate Limiting] --> ON
  end

  classDef box stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,fill:#f9f9f9;
